@EndNode


@Node Problems "Known problems"
                            @{b}Known problems
                            ==============@{ub}

  @{b}OpenGL@{ub} is set off by default. To set it on change @{"tool types" Link "ToolTypes"} or edit @{"dgenrc" Link "Configuring"}.

  @{b}Doublebuffer@{ub} is set off by default. To set it on edit @{"dgenrc" Link "Configuring"}. Leaving
  this off might cause performance problems with fullscreen.

  If you find any other problems please @{"send bug report" Link "Contact"}.

@EndNode


@Node ChangeLog "ChangeLog"
                        @{b}ChangeLog
                        =========@{ub}

 @{b}git-20130524@{ub}

  · Added tool types when launching from Ambient.
  · Added file request for ROM selecting when launching from Ambient.
  · Endianness fix for 32bit conversion to scanline draw
  · Endianness fixes for splash
  · Changes to file handling
  · Quick hack to make debugger work
  · Support for packed ROMs
    · Works with lha, zip, bz2 and gz. tar can also be used.
    · If package contains several roms, only the firstly added is loaded.
  · Added Makefile for MorphOS
    · Checking for OpenGL with autotools didn't work very well with MorphOS.
  · Added MegaDrive2 @{"icons" Links Icons}

@EndNode

@Node Future "Future"
                        @{b}Future
                        ======@{ub}

  · Solve OpenGL on/off problem some user friendlier way
  · Debugger needs different implementation. Currently leaks are possible.
  · Update when ever there is something new available

  If you have new ideas please @{"let me know" Link "Contact"}.

